Abuja – A man who claims to have been faithful to his wife all along was stunned about what he read on her mobile phone when he gained access to it. Relationship adviser and blogger, Joro Olumofin has shared the story of a man who secretly unlocked the mobile phone of his wife. According to him, the woman is flirting with her colleague who is also married. From their conversations, they have kissed and the man is making moves to sleep with her. He is presently heartbroken and also unsure of recovering from the shock. Read the story below: Source